        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "On macOS, FreeBSD, OpenBSD, and Windows, the full exit code reported by",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "the process is reported to the parent process. Linux and other POSIX-like",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "systems may only reliably report the low unsigned 8 bits (0–255) of",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "the exit code.",
